( Carnage: I am deeply sorry if I had not posted for the past while. I have 
had to add and detete a few programs on my computer and doing so has not 
been the best.
Though, I am glad to see you are back steph.)

** Carnage listened easily to Instrat, wondering if she could trust a bot 
which had tried to rip her head off one moment and be totally calm the next.
It just didn't feel right.
Carnage backed up a step.**

" So, you just go around trying to kill people just because they're there?"

** She had lowered her gun but she could aim it towards Instrat and fire 
more quickly then amy bot could blink.
But then Carnage caught Teltili's little action of a lunatic and a tiny 
smile crossed her face, thinking that only this woman could be this 
lighthearted at a time like this!
Carnage simply shrugged before she looked back towards Instrat...just in 
time to see a rather large glob of something white and green drop from out 
of nowhere towards his head.
She looked up and spotted a rather large raptor( bird of prey) sitting just 
above the bot.
A wide smile crossed her lips before the she looked back towards Instrat, 
covering her mouth with one hand and the side of her gun as she tried to 
keep herself from laughing. Doing a very bad job at it.
That was SO funny!
Perfect timing!
Carnage finally gave up and began laughing, shaking her head and waving her 
hand at Instrat.**

" I'm sorry! I...was just thinking of something funny!"

** Of course she wasn't about to tell Instrat that there was a squish of 
poop plumiting towards his head.
That would ruin the extremely funny outcome.**
